      <title>特朗普上任第二周考验他对国会的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-second-week-in-office-tests-his-influence-over-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统刚刚用记号笔签发了一系列行政命令，本周他开始拉拢、哄骗和强迫立法部门的成员支持他的议程和内阁人选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-second-week-in-office-tests-his-influence-over-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
