    <item>
      <title>特朗普与斯塔默就职以来首次通话讨论贸易问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-and-starmer-discuss-trade-on-first-call-since-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相凯尔·斯塔默与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在特朗普重返白宫后的首次通话中讨论了贸易问题。双方还同意“尽快会面”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-and-starmer-discuss-trade-on-first-call-since-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 21:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙人质问题解决 以色列、黎巴嫩延长停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/israel-s-ceasefire-deals-face-test-with-impasse-on-gaza-refugees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府周日表示，以色列和黎巴嫩同意将停火延长至 2 月 18 日，以便以色列军队有更多时间撤军，同时加沙与哈马斯因人质问题引发的争端得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/israel-s-ceasefire-deals-face-test-with-impasse-on-gaza-refugees</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 19:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因移民争端对哥伦比亚征收关税、实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-slaps-tariffs-travel-ban-on-colombia-in-migrant-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在哥伦比亚左翼总统拒绝允许两架载有被驱逐移民的军用飞机降落几个小时后，唐纳德·特朗普总统对哥伦比亚实施了关税和制裁，以惩罚美国盟友哪怕只是部分违背他的移民目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-slaps-tariffs-travel-ban-on-colombia-in-migrant-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:41:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普高层官员抵达芝加哥启动移民打击行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/acting-deputy-ag-head-visits-chicago-to-observe-immigration-enforcement-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥（美联社）——包括“边境沙皇”汤姆·霍曼和代理司法部副部长在内的特朗普政府高级官员周日访问了芝加哥，见证了加强移民执法的开始]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/acting-deputy-ag-head-visits-chicago-to-observe-immigration-enforcement-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 16:55:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢卡申科在白俄罗斯选举中延长执政 被指虚假</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/lukashenko-set-to-extend-power-in-highly-controlled-belarus-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白俄罗斯总统亚历山大·卢卡申科在一次严格控制的投票中延长了自己的任期，在没有遇到任何反对的情况下，欧盟称之为“骗局”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/lukashenko-set-to-extend-power-in-highly-controlled-belarus-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 09:12:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和黎巴嫩延长撤军期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/2-killed-in-lebanon-amid-protests-as-israeli-forces-remain-after-withdrawal-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩迈斯贾巴尔（美联社）——据黎巴嫩卫生官员报道，周日，黎巴嫩南部的以色列军队向要求他们按照停火协议撤军的抗议者开火，造成至少 22 人死亡，124 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/2-killed-in-lebanon-amid-protests-as-israeli-forces-remain-after-withdrawal-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 08:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
